  "detailed_description": "Someday any kingdom comes to an end. Most often this is due to wars, but what if it happens because of magic?<br>It is a question of one kingdom, whose king was cursed by an evil shaman. All would be nothing, but our hero is the brother of that very king. What to do, save a brother or seek a shaman? <strong>In this world, you choose what you do</strong>.<br>Game process:<br>- 20+ locations;<br>- 10+ different kinds of enemies;<br>- 1 story and 2+ minor quests;<br>- Battles in the style of classical jrpg.",
